If you are interested in tipping a hat of gratitude, if you like games or game shows, please check out my inexpensive selection of game show books on Amazon: https://t.co/QrA6XsWbRQ
They’re fun, I promise!
Thanks, everyone, for all of the good times since 2014. 
- @ChadMosher

Today is the final day @CoolJepStories posts a fresh set of #Jeopardy stories. I want to thank the 10,400 of you who have followed this page and found some sort of enjoyment in the way I framed the oddest 2 minutes in television.
And thanks to original co-founder @AJMandracchia.

Hi all,
I wanted to let everyone know that Friday, July 26th, the last day of @Jeopardy! season 35, will be the final day @CoolJepStories posts a new story.
It’s been fun to see this account grow over the last 5 years, but I think the time has now come to move on.
❤️- @ChadMosher
